                <span itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Morning Agenda: Glencore Is Said to Plan Debt Investor Meeting</span>
                <span class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
                    By Amie Tsang                </span>
                <!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2015-09-30T09:56:13+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">September 30, 2015 5:56 am</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">September 30, 2015 5:56 am</span>            </div>
			<div class="entry-content">
			<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//news.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/09/30/morning-agenda-glencore-is-said-to-plan-debt-investor-meeting/" data-title="Morning Agenda: Glencore Is Said to Plan Debt Investor Meeting" data-description="UBS Fined Over Puerto Rico Funds | The War Over Corporate Governance | The Drone Company Ready for Spin-off">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
